987
01:06:12,984 --> 01:06:14,736
But we all have doubts.

988
01:06:14,819 --> 01:06:18,406
Doubts about our powers -
Are we worthy of them?

989
01:06:18,490 --> 01:06:20,492
Do we have the right to use them?

990
01:06:20,575 --> 01:06:23,161
After all, what is good...

991
01:06:23,953 --> 01:06:25,997
