993
01:06:29,751 --> 01:06:32,462
Scarlet Witch and Dr. Pretorius both agree.

994
01:06:33,546 --> 01:06:35,507
What you did was not treasonous.

995
01:06:35,590 --> 01:06:37,592
Forgive yourself.

996
01:06:37,676 --> 01:06:39,761
Don't judge your own actions so harshly.

997
01:06:43,640 --> 01:06:44,933
(electricity crackles)

998
01:06:45,016 --> 01:06:47,018
Don't you understand?

999
01:06:47,102 --> 01:06:48,770
This is no mistake.

1000
01:06:48,853 --> 01:06:52,941
I have been double-crossing the Alliance
for a very long time now

1001
01:06:53,024 --> 01:06:56,319
and reporting directly to Sargon.

1002
01:06:56,403 --> 01:06:58,405
And you know why?

1003
01:06:59,614 --> 01:07:02,909
Because I am madly in love with him.

1004
01:07:03,952 --> 01:07:06,371
<i>Do you remember
when he attacked our guild's outpost?</i>

1005
01:07:06,454 --> 01:07:09,541
<i>I tried to fight him then,
but I was alone and I failed.</i>

1006
01:07:09,624 --> 01:07:11,376
