1014
01:07:31,855 --> 01:07:33,565
I fell in love with him.

1015
01:07:33,648 --> 01:07:35,275
I refuse to believe this.

1016
01:07:35,358 --> 01:07:38,069
Sargon is not a mutant,
but he understands mutant desire.

1017
01:07:38,153 --> 01:07:41,072
I became his lover.
It's the only reason he set me free.

1018
01:07:41,156 --> 01:07:44,409
You are crazy. Sargon loves no one.

1019
01:07:44,492 --> 01:07:47,245
