1025
01:08:23,364 --> 01:08:24,991
And place your bets, please.

1026
01:08:25,074 --> 01:08:27,577
(ball rolling)

1027
01:08:29,454 --> 01:08:31,623
The last bets, thank you.
No more bets.

1028
01:08:31,706 --> 01:08:33,708
<i>Rien ne va plus.</i>

1029
01:08:34,501 --> 01:08:36,586
Twenty-eight, black.

1030
01:08:42,801 --> 01:08:44,803
And five places here.

1031
01:08:45,804 --> 01:08:47,347
Place your bets, please.

1032
01:08:55,104 --> 01:08:56,731
Nine, red.

1033
01:08:59,692 --> 01:09:01,653
Place your bets, please.

1034
01:09:01,736 --> 01:09:05,490
Well, I stayed because of you,
but I could feel my brain cells dying,

1035
01:09:05,573 --> 01:09:06,908
one by one.

1036
01:09:06,991 --> 01:09:08,993
Okay, but you don't find her amazing?

1037
01:09:09,994 --> 01:09:11,913
I think she's totally fascinating.

1038
01:09:11,996 --> 01:09:13,873
It's such a stupid character. Come on.

1039
01:09:13,957 --> 01:09:16,751
Because it takes place on a spaceship?

1040
01:09:16,835 --> 01:09:20,547
I know that if it was set on an assembly line
or like a farm or something,

1041
01:09:20,630 --> 01:09:21,756
you'd love it.

1042
01:09:21,840 --> 01:09:25,218
It's true. I have a hard time
taking bimbos in astronaut suits

